### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api

###
### Standard API Response Format:
### {
###   "status": int,           // HTTP status code
###   "message": string,        // Success or error message
###   "data": {} / [],          // Response data (object or array)
###   "paging": {               // Optional: for paginated responses
###     "size": int,
###     "page": int,
###     "total_page": int,
###     "total_item": int
###   },
###   "error": {} / []          // Optional: error details
### }
###

### 1. Get CSRF Token (harus dipanggil dulu sebelum register/login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/csrf-token

### Response Example:
### {
###   "status": 200,
###   "message": "CSRF token generated successfully",
###   "data": null,
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }


### 2. Register User (Perlu CSRF Token dari cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-TOKEN: <copy-from-cookie>

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": 2
}

### Response Example (Success):
### {
###   "status": 201,
###   "message": "User registered successfully",
###   "data": {
###     "id": "guid",
###     "username": "admin",
###     "role": 2,
###     "createdAt": "2026-02-16T...",
###     "updatedAt": null
###   },
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }


### 3. Login User (JWT disimpan di cookie "JWT-TOKEN")
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Response Example (Success):
### {
###   "status": 200,
###   "message": "Login successful",
###   "data": {
###     "id": "guid",
###     "username": "admin",
###     "role": 2,
###     "createdAt": "2026-02-16T...",
###     "updatedAt": null
###   },
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }


### 4. Get User Info (otomatis membaca JWT dari cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/info

### Response Example (Success):
### {
###   "status": 200,
###   "message": "User info retrieved successfully",
###   "data": {
###     "id": "guid",
###     "username": "admin",
###     "role": 2,
###     "createdAt": "2026-02-16T...",
###     "updatedAt": null
###   },
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }


### 5. Logout (menghapus JWT cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout

### Response Example (Success):
### {
###   "status": 200,
###   "message": "Logged out successfully",
###   "data": null,
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }


###
### Error Response Examples:
###

### Invalid Input:
### {
###   "status": 400,
###   "message": "Invalid input",
###   "data": null,
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": ["Username is required", "Password must be at least 6 characters"]
### }

### Unauthorized:
### {
###   "status": 401,
###   "message": "Invalid username or password",
###   "data": null,
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }

### CSRF Token Error:
### {
###   "status": 403,
###   "message": "Invalid or missing CSRF token",
###   "data": null,
###   "paging": null,
###   "error": null
### }

###
### Untuk testing mutating requests dengan CSRF protection:
### POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE ke endpoint lain harus mengirim X-CSRF-TOKEN header
###

### Example: Protected POST request
POST {{baseUrl}}/some-protected-endpoint
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-TOKEN: <copy-from-cookie>

{
  "data": "example"
}
